result.formatted_address: 8 Hung Luen Rd, Hung Hom Bay, Hong Kong
result.name: Kowloon Harbourfront Hotel

reviews.text: Rooms have stunning view and good space but are in need of an upgrade. Breakfast was very average.  The Pool was good but closed for 4 out of our 7 day stay, asking around this is quite common. For anyone thinking of booking for the pool i advise you to at least make sure it's open first.
The room had such a great view and enough space. Staff were helpful and friendly. Enjoyed our stay

Great for our needs. Housekeeping was great and staff all answered what we needed. Yeah, more fruit for breakfast but was satisfied with what they had.

Don't expect the flashiest of rooms. The gym is decent and the clubhouse is great. Preferred to use the showers in the gym bathroom than our room as you don't have risk of first flooding the bathroom from the shower curtain not pulled properly. 

Pool is massive. The shuttle was ideal and consistent every 20 mins. Saved us a lot of time and was convenient.
Decent hotel. Room was tidy but dirty and in serious need of renovations. Lobby was nice, and the continental breakfast needs some fruit as there was none there
2nd time staying at this hotel, good rooms for families. Convenient location, good service and shuttle bus really good. Cons restaurant could have more selection but plenty nearby.

result.name: 九龍海灣酒店

reviews.text: Rooms have stunning view and good space but are in need of an upgrade. Breakfast was very average.  The Pool was good but closed for 4 out of our 7 day stay, asking around this is quite common. For anyone thinking of booking for the pool i advise you to at least make sure it's open first.

ホテル料金が高い香港で、家族連れで泊まるならお手頃で結構いいんじゃないでしょうか。ホテルライフを楽しみたい方向けでは全くありません。

フロントの応対はごく普通、ベルボーイの方もテキパキ。館内は清潔感があり、部屋も然り。泊まった部屋は狭い2LDKで合理的、機能的な造り。冷凍冷蔵庫、電子レンジ付き。シャワーとトイレは隣同士でいくら気を付けてシャワー使ってもトイレの周りまで水浸しになりました、そういう造りなんだと諦めました。

3月に行きましたが毎日部屋に帰ると16度設定だったかでエアコンをガンガンかけられていたのには閉口しました。暑くない時期に行くと、部屋が寒いです。

夜は窓から少し夜景も見えました。

キッズルームにはボールプールと滑り台があり、小さめの幼児を短時間遊ばせるにはいいと思います。

場所はどちらかというと不便ですが、それを知った上で行けば何とかなると思います。尖沙咀はペニンシュラの裏まで無料のシャトルバスで10分程度で行けますし、ホンハム駅まで歩いて行けない距離じゃない、私は行かなかったが。タクシー利用もできるし香港島なら5〜6分歩けばフェリーがある。

フェリーにも続くホテル前の海沿い遊歩道は香港島が見渡せてなかなかの景色。地元の人も走ってたり話し込んでたりと、のんびりした雰囲気。

ホテルの朝食はあまりいいレビューが見当たらず付けなかったので、前日に買い込んで部屋で食べました。

色々レビューを見た上でデポジットが要らないとこなのかなと思って行きましたが、必要でした。

一人では利用しませんが、また家族で行くことがあれば有力な候補です。
The room had such a great view and enough space. Staff were helpful and friendly. Enjoyed our stay

Great for our needs. Housekeeping was great and staff all answered what we needed. Yeah, more fruit for breakfast but was satisfied with what they had.

Don't expect the flashiest of rooms. The gym is decent and the clubhouse is great. Preferred to use the showers in the gym bathroom than our room as you don't have risk of first flooding the bathroom from the shower curtain not pulled properly. 

Pool is massive. The shuttle was ideal and consistent every 20 mins. Saved us a lot of time and was convenient.
Decent hotel. Room was tidy but dirty and in serious need of renovations. Lobby was nice, and the continental breakfast needs some fruit as there was none there
